    <!-- ENGLISH -->
    <h2>1. Data Controller</h2>
    <p>Christine Bork<br>Jaco, Costa Rica<br>Email: <a href="mailto:info@zercy.app">info@zercy.app</a></p>

    <h2>2. What Zercy does with your data</h2>
    <p>Zercy is an AI-powered travel planning tool. When you use the tool at <a href="https://zercy.app">app.zercy.app</a>, your travel queries are processed to generate travel recommendations.</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Travel queries you type</strong> are sent to the Anthropic API (Claude AI) and to SerpAPI (for live flight data). They are not stored by Zercy beyond the duration of your session.</li>
      <li><strong>No account is required.</strong> We do not collect your name, email address, or any personal information.</li>
      <li><strong>No tracking cookies.</strong> We do not use advertising trackers or analytics beyond basic server logs provided by our hosting provider (Vercel).</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Third-party services</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Anthropic (Claude API)</strong> — processes your travel queries to generate AI responses. <a href="https://www.anthropic.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Anthropic Privacy Policy</a></li>
      <li><strong>SerpAPI</strong> — retrieves live flight search data from Google Flights. <a href="https://serpapi.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SerpAPI Privacy Policy</a></li>
      <li><strong>Vercel</strong> — hosts this website and may collect basic server access logs (IP address, browser type). <a href="https://vercel.com/legal/privacy-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Vercel Privacy Policy</a></li>
    </ul>

    <h2>4. Affiliate links & partner networks</h2>
    <p>Zercy displays links to third-party booking platforms (for example Booking.com, Expedia, Kayak, Google Flights, Google Hotels, DiscoverCars). Some of these are <strong>affiliate links</strong>: if you book through them, Zercy may receive a commission. The price you pay stays exactly the same — no markup, no hidden fee.</p>
    <p>When you click an affiliate link, you leave Zercy and enter the partner's website. At that point the partner's own privacy policy and cookie practices apply. Affiliate networks may set a tracking cookie on the partner's domain to attribute your booking to Zercy. Zercy does not read or store these cookies.</p>
    <p>Networks Zercy uses or plans to use:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Awin</strong> (for booking.com and others) — <a href="https://www.awin.com/us/legal/privacy-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Privacy Policy</a></li>
      <li><strong>CJ Affiliate (Commission Junction)</strong> — <a href="https://www.cj.com/legal/privacy-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Privacy Policy</a></li>
      <li><strong>DiscoverCars Affiliate</strong> (direct) — <a href="https://www.discovercars.com/affiliate-conditions" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Program Terms</a></li>
    </ul>
    <p>You can opt out of affiliate tracking by simply not clicking the partner buttons and instead visiting the partner's site directly, or by using your browser's tracking prevention.</p>

    <h2>5. Your rights (GDPR)</h2>
    <p>If you are located in the European Economic Area (EEA), you have the right to access, rectify, or erase any personal data we hold about you, as well as the right to data portability and to lodge a complaint with your local data protection authority.</p>
    <p>Since we do not store personal data from your searches, there is typically no personal data for us to provide or delete. If you have any questions, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@zercy.app">info@zercy.app</a>.</p>

    <h2>6. Cookies</h2>
    <p>Zercy itself uses only technically necessary cookies (e.g. to remember that you closed the cookie banner, via localStorage). Vercel may set technical cookies necessary for the website to function.</p>
    <p>When you click an <strong>affiliate partner link</strong>, the partner's website (e.g. Booking.com, Expedia, DiscoverCars) and the affiliate network (Awin, CJ) may set their own cookies on their own domains. These are not set by Zercy. You can control them through your browser settings or by not clicking the partner buttons.</p>

    <h2>7. Changes to this policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. The current version is always available at <a href="https://zercy.app/privacy">zercy.app/privacy</a>.</p>

    <h2>8. Contact</h2>
    <p>For any privacy-related questions: <a href="mailto:info@zercy.app">info@zercy.app</a></p>

